{"type": "article", "id": 24004, "title": "可节约空间的衣架", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-17T07:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 69, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122137OevEpmJfSxd5Vzsi.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款衣架想要为衣柜腾出更多的空间。设计师发现，传统的三角衣架使衣服和晾衣杆之间有很大空隙，通过改变衣架的形状，可以让衣服“调高”，以空出衣服下面真正有用的部分，就可以用来放鞋了。他制作了带天鹅绒表层和合成木两种，前者可以更好防滑，后者的使用时间更长。产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/higherhangers/higher-hangers-space-saving-closet-organization-re?utm_source=higherhangers.com&amp;utm_medium=l%3Cem%3E%3C/em%3Eink&amp;utm_co%3Cem%3E%3C/em%3Entent=higherhangers_l%3Cem%3E%3C/em%3Eink&amp;utm_campaign=kspledges\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122132Xlsh68MULZ1w4IPg.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.51323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122132kNaWxr8mpzMPi6nt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.40220049\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122133bDZfPvitgEoyW1uG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46821516\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122133J4Tj6sKePyc1Dw0h.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122135cv7f4sglHjbGDJFP.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71764706\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}